<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p>在刚刚过去的8月</p>
<p>据省气候中心监测</p>
<p>全省平均气温29.1℃</p>
<p>较常年同期异常偏高2.0℃</p>
<p>为1978年以来第二高</p>
<p>仅次于2013年</p>
<p>其中沿淮淮北中西部、江淮之间大部</p>
<p>及沿江江南东部异常偏高2.0～3.1℃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然白露如期而至</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>可是今明两天</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“秋老虎”强势上山</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">炎热又将重新笼罩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200906/c7bb758b81454d338e667c362d51893a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>安徽省天气预报</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">↓↓↓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">7-8日淮北部分和淮河以南</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大部分地区将出现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">35℃左右的高温天气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200906/df1d7e5bb00d40de83bbe5807cdf0587.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">9-12日受冷空气影响</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">全省平均气温将下降3～5℃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200906/2c06f495b13d4056b365e6dabe44c269.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>阜阳天气预报</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">↓↓↓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">据市气象部门预计</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">未来一周</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我市以晴好天气为主</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>今明两天最高气温达到35℃</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好在这样的天气持续时间较短</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>9-12日受冷空气影响</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>平均气温将下降3～5℃</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一周具体天气↓</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200906/da685c4638bb4eaaa4842dc4a847a41e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长夏终将逝去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凉秋不久可期</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有个重要提醒一定要注意！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">↓↓↓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“处暑十八盆，白露勿露身”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“白露身不露，着凉易泻肚”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“白露勿露身，早晚要叮咛”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">意思说的都是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">白露之后昼夜温差很大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果这时再赤膊露体</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就容易受凉，轻则易患感冒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">重则易染肺疾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200906/2685243b63dc45708966ed84d723d1aa.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">白露养生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">需注意以下几方面的调养</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">↓↓↓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>精神调养</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此时勿使情绪波动太大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要保持情绪稳定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宁神定志，以免影响肺气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>良好的情绪调控</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>可以令人身心愉悦</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>起居调养</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">白露早晚温差最大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然入睡时分气温并不是很低</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但渐渐降低的温度夹带着丝丝凉气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>盖好被子不让身体外露</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>以免身体着凉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>运动调养</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">运动量及运动强度可较夏天适当加大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可选择慢跑、打太极拳、体操</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打篮球、羽毛球等</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>以汗出但不疲倦为度</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这样有助于机体内气血调畅</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>饮食调养</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要注意预防秋燥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>多吃辛润食物</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如梨、百合、甘蔗、芋头、</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">沙葛、萝卜、银耳、蜜枣等</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>也可结合药膳进行调理</strong></p>
<p><strong>"过了白露，长衣长裤。"</strong></p>
<p><strong>早晚温差大</strong></p>
<p><strong>诸君勿忘添衣裳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>扩散提醒身边人！</strong></p>